contribute greatly to coordinating the training agenda across Europe too.

We are committed in ELIXIR-UK to find the best applicants for these
posts.  We will consider applicants who might bridge between our
ELIXIR-UK partners by, for example, working remotely from the post’s
host institution, i.e. Oxford.

